     DDDDEEEESSSSCCCCRRRRIIIIPPPPTTTTIIIIOOOONNNN
          The _x_t_w_i_d utility is an interactive drawing program that
          runs on AT&T Dot-Mapped Display terminals (5620 DMD and 630
          MTG).  The terminal must be operating in the layers environ-
          ment before downloading _x_t_w_i_d [see _l_a_y_e_r_s(_1)].  It allows
          the user to draw and "paint" pictures with the mouse.

          The ----VVVV option causes _x_t_w_i_d to print a message that identi-
          fies which version it is.

          The ----cccc option specifies that _x_t_w_i_d is to be stored in the
          terminal's application cache.  It is only available for the
          630 MTG.

