          Buttons 1 and 2 are used for drawing. The drawing modes can
          be changed by selecting an option on the bbbbuuuuttttttttoooonnnnssss menu (see
          bbbbuuuuttttttttoooonnnnssss below).  Button 3 raises the "supermenu" (a menu
          with menus as selections).

