          The _x_t_w_i_d utility has six functional menus.  All are options
          on the Supermenu.  Each is described below:

          ssssttttyyyylllleeee     This functional menu permits the user to choose
                    from a variety of drawing tools.

          tttteeeexxxxttttuuuurrrreeee   This functional menu allows the user to use a
                    group of textures as "paint" and also to create
                    his or her own textures.

          bbbbrrrruuuusssshhhh     This functional menu allows the user to select
                    from a variety of brush sizes and also lets the
                    user create their own.

          bbbbuuuuttttttttoooonnnnssss   This functional menu lets the user determine the
                    storage modes that buttons one and two use for
                    drawing (OOOORRRR, XXXXOOOORRRR, CCCCLLLLEEEEAAAARRRR, SSSSTTTTOOOORRRREEEE; these correspond
                    to the logical functions or, exclusive-or, clear
                    and copy).

          ccccooooppppyyyy      This functional menu permits the user to copy and
                    rotate portions of the layer.

